replies.body:
That attack speed steroid is actually pretty weak when you compare it to other ADCs, such as:

{{champion:18}} 
Q- 30/50/70/90/110%

{{champion:96}} 
Q Passive- 15/20/25/30/35% all the time

{{champion:21}} 
W- 40/55/70/85/100%

{{champion:222}} 
Q- 30/40/50/60/70%-100/110/120/130/140% after 3 attacks based on level

{{champion:15}} 
R- 30/45/60% while W is active

{{champion:110}} 
Passive- 40% (+50% bonus attack speed) bonus attack speed on champion takedown, 20% (+25% bonus attack speed) bonus attack speed on any other kill

It's pretty tame in comparison. In truth, I find her pretty underwhelming in comparison to many other ADCs. However, that's just my opinion.
